name: HonoluluGuide
0:
”Alexa, ask honolulu guide what are the top five things to do”
”Alexa, ask honolulu guide to give me an attraction”
”Alexa, ask honolulu guide to get me the news”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: honolulu guide
des:
This Alexa skill provides top 5 attractions and top 5 things to do while in Honolulu. It also provides the 3 top latest local news headline courtesy of the New York Times.

Some examples of things you could ask are:

Tell me about Honolulu. 
Give me an attraction.
Tell me the top five things to do. 
Tell me the local news. 
What would you like to do?

For comments and feedbacks please email siyuanpfx@gmail.com
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
